        <i> a masterpiece.</i>         

557
00:33:53,399 --> 00:33:55,065
       <i> Have you seen it?</i>       
        <i> Who's seen it?</i>         

558
00:33:55,067 --> 00:33:56,533
     <i> What's the good word?</i>     
