569
00:34:18,390 --> 00:34:21,825
         I'm just tired of being
         two different people.  

570
00:34:21,827 --> 00:34:23,460
             I played that game 
             at Princeton       

571
00:34:23,462 --> 00:34:25,395
           and I played it again
           at Harvard.          

572
00:34:25,397 --> 00:34:28,532
 There were white kids at school
