596
00:35:25,691 --> 00:35:27,524
    - the grunt work, right?    
    -<i> Right.</i>                    

597
00:35:27,526 --> 00:35:29,893
      But if I don't speak up,  
      what's the alternative?   

598
00:35:29,895 --> 00:35:32,162
              Shut my mouth     
              and sit there     
              looking pretty?   

599
00:35:32,164 --> 00:35:34,264
      First of all,             
      you always sit there      
      looking pretty.           

600
00:35:34,266 --> 00:35:37,501
         <i> Second of all,</i>        
         <i> I'm not suggesting</i>    
         <i> you silence yourself.</i> 

601
00:35:37,503 --> 00:35:40,670
       I'm just wondering       
       why you chose to work    
       at a corporate firm      

602
00:35:40,672 --> 00:35:43,440
  where you knew your silence   
  would be expected.            

603
00:35:43,442 --> 00:35:47,444
 And, really, what I'm wondering
 is why you're wasting the fight
 you have inside you            

604
00:35:47,446 --> 00:35:50,480
    on battles you can't win    
    and issues you don't        
    care about.                 

605
00:35:52,184 --> 00:35:53,483
                 Excuse me?     

606
00:35:55,187 --> 00:35:58,255
      You think because we spend
      one afternoon together    

607
00:35:58,257 --> 00:36:00,157
           and you tried        
           to buy me a sandwich,

608
00:36:00,159 --> 00:36:01,625
             you're entitled    
             to pass judgment   

609
00:36:01,627 --> 00:36:03,460
          on the choices I made 
          in my life?           

610
00:36:03,462 --> 00:36:06,363
     - ( sighs )                
     - You think                
       I'm wasting my life.     

611
00:36:06,365 --> 00:36:07,531
              <i> Now, I never used</i>
              <i> those words.</i>     

612
00:36:07,533 --> 00:36:09,566
        You didn't have         
        to use those words.     

613
00:36:09,568 --> 00:36:13,170
<i> You used other ones,</i>           
<i> and they stung just as much.</i>   

