00:36:14,540 --> 00:36:15,906
       If you really loved      
       what you were doing,     

616
00:36:15,908 --> 00:36:17,707
      would you be bothered     
      by what I said?           

617
00:36:17,709 --> 00:36:19,609
                         <i> No.</i>   

